 # v9 — EdgeJS Browser Runtime Build
 #
 # Targets:
 #   make setup       — install Emscripten SDK + dependencies
 #   make fetch       — clone EdgeJS source + node-wasix32 shims
 #   make configure   — run CMake with Emscripten toolchain
